title: The Cluckin’ Bell Farm Raid
headline: The Cluckin’ Bell Farm Raid
subtitle: Now Available
content:
What’s Cluckin’ Bell’s flavor of the month? Turns out it’s cocaine, courtesy of a new cartel in town working hand-in-glove with the LSPD.

Take advantage of institutional corruption to make serious bank, alongside your man on the inside: officer Vincent Effenburger. The Cluckin’ Bell Farm Raid is now available.
